## Fits the system

- **Frontier now**: an always-on glob-scoped rule the agent applies whenever editing Python under `pi-sidecar/app/**`. A future `pisidecar-pydantic-auditor` subagent (tracked separately if rule enforcement gaps emerge in practice) would automate the audit-side check; until then, the rule itself is the enforcement layer.
- **Local subagents (future)**: the read-first list for a hypothetical `pisidecar-pydantic-auditor` is small — route files under `pi-sidecar/app/web/` plus the contracts module — making it a clean candidate when one is opened.
